TEXT.TITLE: DELIVERABLE GRADE GUIDE
TEXT.BODY: graded grain meeting exchange quality requirements for futures delivery, excluding CCC-owned grain. Includes all non-CCC deliverable grades regardless of whether receipted and/or registered. Non-del. Grades/Ungraded - Graded grain not meeting exchange quality requirements for futures delivery and ungraded grain, excluding CCC-owned grain. CCC Stocks - grains owned by CCC. Non-deliverable classes or subclasses of grain (e.g. white wheat or white corn) are not included in any of the figures. * year ago data for this category is not available. Reuter
